'''Hoodrat''' is an urban slang term describing a girl with loose morals. A hoodrat can be commonly defined as a synonym for [[slut]], but, more specifically, the word applies to a girl practicing her promiscuity in a small area, or a [[neighbourhood]].
The term was largely used by early 90s hip-hop artists, but received a rejuvenation in recent years by Brooklyn, NY indie rock band, [[The Hold Steady]].
